Title: Object: Souvenir de la campagne de Rosette
Description: View of Egypt (Rosetta?), with palm tree overhanging a river in the centre foreground, and beyond a building with tower and dome; published in 'L'Artiste', 1835, volume IX, page 149 Etching
Curator's comments: The inscription only reads 'Marilhat Pinx.'; whether he etched the plate himself is unsure.
Bibliographic references: IFF / Inventaire du Fonds Français: Bibliothèque Nationale, Département des Estampes (1)
